    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nAB: \\sqrt{3}x + 50 - 20\\sqrt{3} = \\frac{1}{8}x^2 \\Leftrightarrow \\begin{cases} x = 20 \\\\ x = -20 + 8\\sqrt{3} \\end{cases}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
