    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nS = 2. \\int_{-20+8\\sqrt{3}}^{20} \\left( \\sqrt{3}x + 50 - 20\\sqrt{3} - \\frac{1}{8}x^2 \\right) dx \\approx 745 (\\text{cm}^2).\n$$"
